886
00:53:50,470 --> 00:53:52,210
You should be like Tin now.

887
00:54:00,130 --> 00:54:01,730
You're so partial to him.

888
00:54:01,760 --> 00:54:03,000
Do you know him?

889
00:54:03,030 --> 00:54:04,180
No.

890
00:54:05,010 --> 00:54:06,060
But

891
00:54:06,700 --> 00:54:08,090
